room_title: Escape room "The Heist" by The Escape Covington in Covington
room_address: 13433 Seymour Myers Blvd, Suite 4 Covington, LA 70433
room_description: In November of 2015, diamond lovers from across the globe converged on the National Gallery to view the rarely exhibited Cullen 1 Diamond. Upon the gallery opening, museum officials are stunned to find the Cullen 1 missing. With nowhere to turn, the gallery hires you along with a team of renowned private investigators to hunt down and retrieve the priceless gem.
